'''''Adams Apples''''' ni urukurikirane rw'amafilime yo muri Gana, yakinwe na Yvonne Okoro, Joselyn Dumas, John Dumelo, Naa Ashorkor Mensa-Doku, Anima Misa Amoah, Adjetey Anang, Helene Asante, SoulKnight Jazz, Jasmine Baroudi, Vincent McCauley, Roselyn Ngissah, Fred Kanebi.  Urukurikirane rugizwe na firime icumi zerekana amakinamico, azwi ku izina rya "chapters", yakozwe na Ken Attoh kandi iyobowe na Shirley Frimpong-Manso . 

Urukurikirane film bukurikira ubuzima mu muryango wa Adam , bakaba bagizwe na Doris Adams (Anima Misa Amoah), umupfakazi wa ikintu KALIMANZIRA umudiplomate, n'abakobwa be batatu; Baaba ( Okoro ), Jennifer ( Dumas ) na Kuukua ( Mensah-Doku ), berekana uburyo bakemura umuryango wabo utoroshye, ubuzima bw'urukundo, amabanga ya buri muntu, ibinyoma no kwicuza. A <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spin-off_(media)" rel="mw:ExtLink" title="Spin-off (media)" class="cx-link" data-linkid="132">spin-off</a> televiziyo drama series, na title kimwe kwerekanwa muri Gashyantare 2013, kandi kuva batangiye airing ku DSTV 's Afurika Magic ; televiziyo yashyizeho nyuma y'umwaka igice cya cumi cy'urukurikirane rwa firime.  

